To be honest,

20
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,280
I was three minutes slower
than Duan Lei.

21
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,560
I've never been so frustrated like this.

22
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:02,960
Since little,

23
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,480
you've been the best boy

24
