31
00:05:44,980 --> 00:05:47,060
(Unit One)

32
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,680
What are you doing here?

33
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,600
Waiting for you.

34
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,720
It's so late. Where have you been?

35
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,040
Where else could I be?

36
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,480
The mill organized for us
to watch synchronized swimming.

37
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,920
I thought you were in the night school.

38
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,440
I waited at the door for a long while

39
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,360
but didn't see you at all.

40
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:14,840
Qi Tian,

41
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,240
don't bother to escort me, seriously.

42
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,440
It's too much trouble for you.

43
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,360
No trouble at all.

44
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,840
Before leaving, Chunsheng asked me

45
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,160
to take care of you and your father.

46
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,640
I have plenty of time, right?

47
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,880
Fine. Now that you're back,

48
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,760
I'm relieved.

49
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,040
Get back home.

50
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,920
I should go.

51
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,640
Bye.

52
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,440
You're back.

53
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,720
Silly man.

54
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,040
I'm already yours.

55
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,640
Why do you still stare like this?

56
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,640
Come.

57
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,880
I was waiting the whole night.

58
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,480
Before you're back,
I couldn't fall asleep.

59
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,840
Come on, hurry.

60
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,520
Zhao Xiaohui, are you insane?

61
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,680
You're insane!

62
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:23,520
Tell me.

63
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,120
Today, I saw a man in the natatorium.

64
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,440
He ran out upon seeing me.

65
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,320
Is he your friend?

66
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,000
Fine.

67
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,800
Let's talk about this.

68
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,080
Zhao Xiaohui.

69
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,080
Zhao Xiaohui,

70
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,920
what happened to you
and your coach today?

71
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,560
Confess!

72
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,480
What?

73
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,080
If you don't believe me, what can I say?

74
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,840
Fine, I believe you.

75
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:49,800
Say it now.

76
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:53,040
You believe me. Really?

77
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,800
Yes.

78
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,520
OK. Let me tell you this.

79
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,080
Today, out there,

80
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,560
nothing happened.

81
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:00,840
So much for this, huh?

82
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,920
Nothing happened?

83
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:06,520
Then why did that coach stroke you?

84
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,360
This is nothing?

85
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,640
Explain this!

86
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:10,800
Heizi,

87
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,720
from what happened
before we got married,

88
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,280
you still haven't
learned your lesson, huh?

89
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:20,800
You want to know this, right?

90
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,560
Fine. Listen.

91
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,760
Well,

92
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,440
I don't know

93
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,600
what your friend told you.

94
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,240
Today, we just performed
for workers of the textile mill.

95
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,600
When it was over,

96
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,480
the coach handed me a bath towel

97
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,440
and stroked me.

98
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,480
I slapped him immediately

99
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,240
and cursed him.

100
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:38,040
Yanqiu was there, too.

101
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,800
If you don't believe me, go ask her.

102
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,760
That's what happened. I'm done.

103
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,360
I believe you.

104
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:55,960
Heizi,

105
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,560
if you always

106
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,640
suspect me like this,

107
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,920
what fun can you find

108
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,680
in our marriage?

109
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,080
Xiaohui,

110
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,480
I'm wrong.

111
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,480
I just didn't dare to think

112
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,320
that you would leave me.

113
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,760
I'm sorry.

114
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,880
I told you.

115
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,320
In my life,

116
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,720
unless you discarded me,

117
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,760
I wouldn't leave you.

118
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,000
What else worries you?

119
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,080
I'm no longer worried.

120
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:47,680
Heizi, whatever you think, let me know.

121
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,880
When we live together,

122
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,960
we shouldn't be sulking.

123
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,960
Understand?

124
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,080
Yes.

125
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,040
Then, let's say it's the last time, OK?

126
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,520
All right. Come up.

127
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,720
Wait.

128
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,560
What?

129
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,720
You move inside.

130
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,960
Or I couldn't see you.

131
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,120
Go, go.

132
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:16,640
Move.

133
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:23,560
Good.

134
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:24,920
Now, I can see you.

135
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:28,560
The... The coach...

136
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,280
Where did he stroke you?

137
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,080
Let me check.

138
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,600
Don't bite me!

139
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,880
Zhao Xiaohui!

140
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:38,800
I really...

