(Wedding)

142
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,040
After the operation,
the patient of Bed No.24 has

143
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,360
(Nurse Station)
pulmonary hypertension

144
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,800
and slight tricuspid regurgitation.

145
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:50,960
Last night, as monitored,

146
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,520
his heart rate was around 100.

147
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,600
The patient of Bed No.26
was in good condition last night.

148
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,280
He went to the toilet twice.

149
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,800
No chest distress after he walked.

150
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,360
This morning, his temperature was normal

151
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,160
with clear pulmonary respiration.

152
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:03,560
His heart rate is 70,

153
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,120
beating regularly without murmur.

154
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,480
OK. Go back for some rest.

155
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:10,200
You've got bloodshot eyes.

156
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,200
See you tomorrow morning.

157
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,480
See you then.

158
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:19,920
I should go. See you tomorrow.

159
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:20,960
See you tomorrow, Xiaomei.

160
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:22,960
Xiaomei, knocking off?

161
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,600
See you tomorrow.

162
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,080
Xiaomei, getting off?

163
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,280
Goodbye.

164
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,040
See you tomorrow.

165
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:33,820
(Be united for greater victories)

166
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,720
There are you, Xiaomei.

167
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:45,960
Yes.

168
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,360
You're just in time.

169
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:53,160
Or I would be late.

170
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,920
I timed it and rushed here.

171
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,280
You must be tired. You're sweating.

172
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,800
It's OK.

173
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,280
I don't know

174
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,200
what our leaders were thinking.

175
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,960
They made us go to the night school.

176
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,520
Luckily, you can help.

177
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,160
If my father stayed at home alone,

178
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,160
I would be worried.

179
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,280
Thank you for these days.

180
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,040
Don't say that.

181
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,320
Chunsheng asked me to take care of you.

182
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:16,200
He just talked

183
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,480
and didn't care
whether it was hard for you.

184
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:18,680
It's not hard.

185
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,440
You bought some vegetables?

186
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:23,400
The money for vegetable shopping

187
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,520
is where it has always been.

188
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,280
In the cookie tin. Take some yourself.

189
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:27,520
No hurry.

190
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,320
Mr. Xiao is sleeping?

191
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:31,440
I'll go make dinner.

192
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,600
He'll be hungry when he wakes up.

193
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,960
He has a good appetite recently.

194
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:37,200
It means he's getting better.

195
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,920
Hope so.

196
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,800
I should go.

197
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:42,560
Wait.

198
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,440
Yanqiu,

199
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,760
why do I feel

200
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,480
you look different today?

201
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,120
I don't.

202
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:53,600
You do.

203
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:54,920
You look prettier.

204
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:57,120
You're wearing a gorgeous scarf.

205
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,600
When I was shopping in Xidan,

206
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:00,440
it was on sale.

207
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:01,680
Then I bought it.

208
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:02,440
Looks great.

209
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,320
Wait, Yanqiu.

210
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,200
You rouged your lips?

211
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:10,360
No. You saw it wrong.

212
00:13:11,680 --> 00:13:12,560
Yanqiu,

213
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,400
is anything going on with you?

214
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,680
Qi Tian told me

215
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,560
a teacher at the night school...

216
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:20,480
Don't trust his blab.

217
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,920
I even hate to think of him.

218
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:25,360
Now,

219
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:27,600
he's like my personal
instructor and commissar.

220
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,680
He keeps asking

221
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,880
where I go or who I meet.

222
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,400
If I meet a man,

223
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,440
I have to tell him.

224
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:36,760
Wait and see.

225
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,760
He'll go to the night school tonight.

226
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,200
Why?

227
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,080
Who's he to me?

228
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,440
Why can he restrain me like that?

229
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,120
Why?

230
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:46,880
Because your brother asked him to.

231
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,960
I wrote several letters
to complain about this,

232
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,960
but he pretended he didn't see.

233
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:52,440
Come on, he has someone watch me.

234
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:54,200
All right. Get going.

235
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,280
Or you'd be late.

236
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:56,680
Oh,

237
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,520
I'll take you to a movie this Sunday.

238
00:13:58,960 --> 00:13:59,560
OK.

239
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:00,560
Thank you.

240
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,440
Mr. Xiao,

241
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,160
you have a better appetite.

242
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,680
When you eat more, you'll recover soon.

243
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,200
You make delicious dishes.

244
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:22,680
Better than Yanqiu.

245
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:26,360
You're just fed up with her dishes.

246
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:27,880
Very well.

247
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:30,600
We can cook in turn
and make different dishes.

248
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,080
Thank you.

249
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,560
My pleasure.

250
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,120
Don't mention it, Mr. Xiao.

251
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:36,480
Stay for some rest.

252
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:37,760
I'll go wash the dishes.

253
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,280
Hongling,

254
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,480
go back to your room for some rest.

255
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:45,200
When Ye is back,
have him do the washing.

256
