262
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:27,760
Come on.

263
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,880
When a man like you stands here,

264
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:32,000
what if she sees you and gets annoyed?

265
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,760
I have something to ask Yanqiu.

266
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:39,840
