267
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,880
And why do you care so much?

268
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,720
Tian, do you have a crush on her?

269
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:46,560
I care about her? I don't.

270
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:48,600
I just fear she would be bullied.

271
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:49,200
And I can't...

272
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,760
I can't explain it to Chunsheng.

