00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:03,280
This course needs more operation.

275
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:05,200
When you're learning,

276
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,120
if you have problems,

277
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,440
come ask me at any time.

278
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,000
It's getting late.

279
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:09,760
Stay safe.

280
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:10,080
OK.

281
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:10,960
Be careful on your way back.

282
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:11,640
Goodbye, Mr. Fan.

283
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:12,320
Goodbye.

284
