411
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:06,960
I beg you.

412
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,080
Don't tell my school leaders.

413
00:21:08,520 --> 00:21:10,000
I'll graduate and have
my job assignment soon.

414
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,360
If this is exposed,

415
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,160
my hard study over all these years

416
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:14,160
will be wasted.

417
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,400
And I'll be doomed.

418
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:16,320
Gentlemen,

419
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:17,280
I beg you.

420
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:18,680
Please be a bigger person

421
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,840
