444
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:24,920
Breadwinner?

445
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:26,800
Or backbone?

446
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:29,920
Can we not even survive without you?

447
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,040
I'm telling you this.

448
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:36,760
Without men, we'd still live a great life.

449
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,120
We don't need

450
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:41,640
this narcissistic care and entanglement.

451
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:46,720
She doesn't have an affair.

452
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:50,000
But if you keep suspecting her,

453
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:51,600
maybe she will.

454
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,440
Yanqiu is right.

455
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:56,960
Yanqiu,

