00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:42,860
Why not?

579
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:45,380
You are

580
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:47,940
too curious and bold.

581
00:28:49,620 --> 00:28:50,700
But they don't sound

582
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:52,100
like disadvantages.

583
00:28:53,060 --> 00:28:54,180
Bold men aren't fit?

584
00:28:55,060 --> 00:28:56,380
Who are fit? Cowards?

585
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:57,820
You have no idea.

586
00:28:58,180 --> 00:28:59,340
Times will change.

587
00:29:00,100 --> 00:29:02,260
A future cadre

588
00:29:02,620 --> 00:29:04,100
has to hold the service consciousness,

589
00:29:04,780 --> 00:29:05,860
do law-based administration,

590
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,100
and be very responsible.

591
00:29:07,100 --> 00:29:08,380
A bold man like you
would easily get in trouble.

592
00:29:09,900 --> 00:29:10,780
I don't understand.

593
00:29:11,660 --> 00:29:13,860
Just trust me. I have good instincts.

594
00:29:14,020 --> 00:29:16,220
Yes, indeed.

595
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:17,900
Since you accurately

596
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:18,900
predicted the college entrance exam

597
00:29:19,340 --> 00:29:20,220
and showed off your instincts,

598
00:29:20,220 --> 00:29:21,260
everyone has been awed.

599
00:29:21,580 --> 00:29:22,780
Since then, you give weighty advice

600
00:29:22,780 --> 00:29:23,860
and no one dares to disagree.

601
00:29:27,660 --> 00:29:29,220
You've been reading War and Peace.

602
00:29:29,420 --> 00:29:30,140
Can you understand it?

603
00:29:33,180 --> 00:29:34,380
You not only give weighty advice.

604
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:35,580
I think you just

605
00:29:35,700 --> 00:29:37,660
look down on people like me.

606
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:39,420
I was a loafer, so what?

607
00:29:39,820 --> 00:29:41,020
Now, I'm a college student.

608
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:42,620
It's normal that I read books.

609
00:29:42,980 --> 00:29:44,020
Or do you think

610
00:29:44,020 --> 00:29:44,980
only privileged students like you

611
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:46,220
of English major

612
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:47,660
can read foreign books?

613
00:29:48,580 --> 00:29:49,460
Come on.

614
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:50,540
Don't push it.

615
00:29:55,300 --> 00:29:57,140
We'll spend our lives together.

616
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,260
Your business is mine

617
00:29:59,660 --> 00:30:00,820
and vice versa.

618
00:30:01,220 --> 00:30:02,340
For something concerning our future,

619
00:30:02,700 --> 00:30:04,060
we should respect each other's opinion

620
00:30:04,180 --> 00:30:05,100
and be very serious.

621
00:30:07,700 --> 00:30:08,980
We're talking about business.

622
00:30:09,820 --> 00:30:11,020
Don't try the sweet talk.

623
00:30:11,260 --> 00:30:12,980
What? You don't like it?

624
00:30:15,260 --> 00:30:17,420
Just listen to me and it won't go wrong.

625
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:22,980
Fine, fine.

626
00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:24,420
I'll listen to you.

627
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:40,180
He's trying so hard.

628
00:30:40,220 --> 00:30:41,020
He runs really a lot.

629
00:30:49,700 --> 00:30:50,300
Duan Lei,

630
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:52,780
is Xiao Chunsheng getting insane?

631
00:30:53,220 --> 00:30:54,660
He doesn't even rest.

632
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:56,220
Quite risking his life.

633
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:08,100
This guy

634
00:31:09,340 --> 00:31:10,460
is fierce enough.

635
00:31:12,860 --> 00:31:13,540
Good.

636
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:43,740
Have some water.

637
00:32:57,900 --> 00:32:58,740
Thanks.

638
00:32:59,020 --> 00:32:59,860
You're welcome.

639
00:33:01,060 --> 00:33:01,940
I quite admire

640
00:33:02,460 --> 00:33:03,820
your hard-bitten spirit.

641
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:05,700
When I first came

642
00:33:06,340 --> 00:33:07,700
and knew you were from Beijing,

643
00:33:09,140 --> 00:33:09,940
I thought you didn't

644
00:33:09,940 --> 00:33:11,540
belong in our world.

645
00:33:11,860 --> 00:33:12,980
I disliked you.

646
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:14,980
Turns out

647
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:16,940
I had a bias.

648
00:33:19,940 --> 00:33:20,740
It's OK.

649
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:23,220
You aren't the only one
who thinks like that.

650
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:25,020
Many people think of Beijing soldiers

651
00:33:25,580 --> 00:33:26,820
with prejudices.

652
00:33:31,380 --> 00:33:32,420
But to be honest,

653
00:33:33,620 --> 00:33:34,820
an opponent like you

654
00:33:36,100 --> 00:33:37,300
makes me feel good.

655
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:43,780
I'm ashamed to say this,

656
00:33:44,740 --> 00:33:46,060
but when I was in the military compound,

657
00:33:46,660 --> 00:33:48,900
I never lost to anyone.

658
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:51,260
You are

659
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:53,740
the first man that has ever defeated me.

660
00:33:58,900 --> 00:33:59,780
Let's be friends.

661
00:34:08,900 --> 00:34:10,580
(Unit One)

662
00:34:10,580 --> 00:34:11,580
It's midnight.

663
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:13,540
Naughty Ye Guohua

664
00:34:13,740 --> 00:34:15,060
and our squad leader

665
00:34:15,260 --> 00:34:16,540
launched an emergency muster.

666
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:19,100
Luckily, you trained me before.

667
00:34:19,860 --> 00:34:21,060
Since I came,

668
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:22,580
I've never slept deeply.

669
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:24,700
I'm always ready for the muster.

670
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:27,740
Others weren't as vigilant as me.

671
00:34:28,540 --> 00:34:30,060
(Dear Father)
Some were too deeply asleep to wake up.

672
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:31,820
Some failed to pack very well

673
00:34:32,060 --> 00:34:33,580
and their things dropped along the way.

674
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:38,620
The generations are declining.

675
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,420
When I was in the army...

676
00:34:41,820 --> 00:34:42,740
But my daughter-in-law,

677
00:34:44,100 --> 00:34:45,380
my son is stronger than them,

678
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:47,260
including the guy who wrote this letter.

679
00:34:53,420 --> 00:34:54,300
In this field training,

680
00:34:54,540 --> 00:34:56,220
we hiked for nearly 30 kilometers.

681
00:34:56,700 --> 00:34:58,860
From before dawn to daybreak.

682
00:34:59,580 --> 00:35:01,340
From the camp to the mountain.

683
00:35:01,980 --> 00:35:02,940
Yunnan is

684
00:35:03,020 --> 00:35:04,500
really different from Beijing.

685
00:35:05,100 --> 00:35:07,540
Mushrooms shoot up in the mountains.

686
00:35:07,940 --> 00:35:09,260
They look very weird

687
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:11,860
and don't even look like mushrooms.

688
00:35:12,220 --> 00:35:13,700
There are all kinds of bugs, too.

689
00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:15,540
At lunch,

690
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:17,700
my squad leader roasted some bugs.

691
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:19,860
A long bug was crisp.

692
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:21,580
And it tasted good.

693
00:35:21,940 --> 00:35:23,220
But after eating some,

694
00:35:23,220 --> 00:35:25,140
I felt a little bit sick.

695
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:26,660
And leeches.

696
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:28,140
Before I came,

697
00:35:28,140 --> 00:35:29,500
Xiaomei warned me

698
00:35:29,940 --> 00:35:31,780
not to be leeched.

699
00:35:32,020 --> 00:35:33,380
I was leeched, though.

700
00:35:35,380 --> 00:35:36,500
When I found the leech,

701
00:35:37,020 --> 00:35:39,100
it was as thick as three fingers.

702
00:35:39,620 --> 00:35:40,660
My condition wasn't serious.

703
00:35:40,860 --> 00:35:41,900
In worse cases,

704
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:43,620
some got a few leeches on their shanks.

705
00:35:44,140 --> 00:35:45,620
So, in the second half of the training,

706
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:47,740
we patted each other

707
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:48,860
with the sole of the shoe.

708
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:55,540
Taking a beautiful fall is better
than wandering aimlessly.

709
00:35:56,540 --> 00:35:57,540
When he's young,

710
00:35:57,620 --> 00:36:00,460
he should go out and experience more.

711
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:20,500
Xiaomei, it's you.

712
00:36:22,220 --> 00:36:24,100
I just read
Chunsheng's letter to Mr. Xiao.

713
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:26,540
Sorry for the trouble.

714
00:36:27,220 --> 00:36:28,220
Didn't I tell you

715
00:36:28,220 --> 00:36:30,260
to review your lessons
and not to come often?

716
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:32,060
I just come once a week

717
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:33,300
to take his blood pressure.

718
00:36:33,300 --> 00:36:34,180
No trouble at all.

719
00:36:35,660 --> 00:36:37,380
Do you not want me to eat here?

720
00:36:38,260 --> 00:36:39,700
Tell me what you would like to eat.

721
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:40,540
I'll make it for you.

722
00:36:41,540 --> 00:36:42,300
I love

723
00:36:42,780 --> 00:36:45,100
the tomato and egg noodles you make.

724
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:47,220
Wait. I'll make some for you.

725
00:36:56,540 --> 00:36:57,580
How are you preparing for the Exam?

726
00:36:57,940 --> 00:36:58,860
Not bad.

727
00:37:01,380 --> 00:37:02,100
Yanqiu,

728
00:37:02,940 --> 00:37:04,100
have you been to another city?

729
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:09,580
Does Beidaihe count?

730
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:16,060
Why did you ask?

731
00:37:18,700 --> 00:37:19,780
When reading Chunsheng's letter,

732
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,420
I found it fun.

733
00:37:22,140 --> 00:37:23,300
Compared to them,

734
00:37:23,860 --> 00:37:25,420
I'm like a frog in the well.

735
00:37:26,700 --> 00:37:29,340
The society isn't what it used to be.

736
00:37:31,260 --> 00:37:31,900
We no longer

737
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:33,180
have to be restricted

738
00:37:33,180 --> 00:37:34,140
in this small place.

739
00:37:35,620 --> 00:37:37,100
Not only Beijing,

740
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:38,060
but all the other cities.

741
00:37:38,060 --> 00:37:39,420
You can go anywhere you want.

742
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:41,140
Don't be jealous of him.

743
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:42,500
When you finish college,

744
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:44,380
you'll see a bigger world than him.

745
00:37:45,660 --> 00:37:48,300
People like me can't go anywhere.

746
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:50,660
But you still have chances.

747
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:52,580
A bigger world is waiting for you.

748
00:37:57,020 --> 00:37:58,340
As long as we want to go out,

749
00:37:58,780 --> 00:38:00,140
we can go out at any time.

750
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:07,780
Actually...

751
00:38:09,420 --> 00:38:11,100
Actually, I'm jealous of you guys.

752
00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:13,500
You're young

753
00:38:13,500 --> 00:38:14,580
and have plenty of chances.

754
00:38:15,620 --> 00:38:17,500
When I was young,

755
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:19,300
I could be nothing but a worker.

756
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:22,740
At this age,

757
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:24,740
I don't have a career

758
00:38:25,060 --> 00:38:26,180
or a husband.

759
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:29,620
Life is really hard.

760
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:34,860
Not getting along well

761
00:38:35,420 --> 00:38:36,540
with the teacher of the night school?

762
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:41,580
You should ask Qi Tian,

763
00:38:41,580 --> 00:38:42,940
the instructor and commissar
my brother got me.

764
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:46,020
Mr. Fan failed the political appraisal.

765
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:49,060
Tian did that as a favor.

766
00:38:49,380 --> 00:38:50,420
What favor?

767
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:52,020
Who needs that?

768
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:53,700
My brother is to blame.

769
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:56,260
He insists on having me watched.

770
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:57,220
No way.

771
00:38:57,340 --> 00:38:58,340
The more I think, the angrier I get.

772
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:00,460
Are you finished?

773
00:39:02,340 --> 00:39:03,140
I'll go wash the dishes.

774
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:04,460
Go to Chunsheng's bedroom

775
00:39:04,460 --> 00:39:05,340
for some paper and a pen.

776
00:39:05,660 --> 00:39:06,740
I'll write to criticize him.

777
00:39:07,420 --> 00:39:08,460
You do it with me.

778
00:39:10,460 --> 00:39:11,740
What a man he got me!

779
00:40:12,140 --> 00:40:13,180
He can't play cards.

780
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:13,860
You know what?

781
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:14,940
(Porter, Loader, Garbage transporter)

782
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:15,420
He'll lose.

783
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:23,180
Come on, sir.

784
00:40:23,260 --> 00:40:24,260
What work do you have?

785
00:40:24,660 --> 00:40:26,100
Sand sieving and plastering.

786
00:40:26,900 --> 00:40:28,700
We guys can do that.

787
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:29,860
OK.

788
00:40:29,940 --> 00:40:30,900
Ten hours.

789
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:31,940
No lunch.

790
00:40:32,540 --> 00:40:32,980
Come on.

791
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:34,260
Another poor job.

792
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:35,820
We can earn very little money.

793
00:40:35,820 --> 00:40:36,700
And you don't even offer lunch.

794
00:40:37,020 --> 00:40:38,100
Guys, break up. Go.

795
00:40:38,100 --> 00:40:39,380
Let's wait for bigger jobs.

796
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:40,300
You can hardly get a worker.

797
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:41,620
Let's continue the cards.

798
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,580
Go on.

799
00:40:43,500 --> 00:40:44,260
Sir,

800
00:40:44,940 --> 00:40:45,780
I'll take the job.

801
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:47,100
OK.

802
00:40:47,620 --> 00:40:48,220
Go.

803
00:40:48,500 --> 00:40:48,940
Go.

804
00:40:53,380 --> 00:40:56,460
One, two, three, four.

805
00:40:58,140 --> 00:41:00,300
You're asked to rest more
but you never listen.

806
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:05,140
Mr. Xiao.

807
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:06,620
Oh, Qi Tian.

808
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:08,860
What are you up to?
Haven't seen you for days.

809
00:41:10,180 --> 00:41:11,340
Just fussing around.

810
00:41:12,140 --> 00:41:12,940
How are you doing?

811
00:41:13,340 --> 00:41:13,860
Good.

812
00:41:14,940 --> 00:41:16,420
But she always restrains me.

813
00:41:16,660 --> 00:41:18,540
When you're here, I can take a breath.

814
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:21,740
Fed up with me, huh?

815
00:41:22,340 --> 00:41:23,300
What do you think?

816
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:24,580
I'm going back to my room for some rest.

817
00:41:37,860 --> 00:41:40,100
Didn't I tell you not to waste money?

818
00:41:40,180 --> 00:41:41,580
Why did you buy some many things again?

819
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:56,060
After the training for three months,

820
00:41:56,420 --> 00:41:57,260
all of you

821
00:41:57,500 --> 00:41:58,340
have become

822
00:41:58,340 --> 00:41:59,820
basically standard Chinese soldiers.

823
00:42:00,860 --> 00:42:01,540
Comrades,

824
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:04,340
your life as recruits will soon be over.

825
00:42:04,700 --> 00:42:05,460
Soon,

826
00:42:06,060 --> 00:42:07,100
you're going

827
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:08,180
to different field forces.

828
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:09,580
The Company decided

829
00:42:10,060 --> 00:42:11,700
to give you two days off

830
00:42:11,900 --> 00:42:13,140
so that you could get enough rest!

831
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:14,220
Thank you, Mr. Ye!

832
00:42:14,220 --> 00:42:18,780
- Nice!
- Yeah!

833
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:20,740
All of you!

834
00:42:22,260 --> 00:42:22,940
Dismiss!

835
00:42:23,540 --> 00:42:25,700
- Here we go!
- Go!

836
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:28,940
Chunsheng.

837
00:42:29,660 --> 00:42:30,620
Go visit Hongling.

838
00:42:30,700 --> 00:42:31,860
It's been a long time.

839
00:42:32,500 --> 00:42:33,620
OK. I'm on my way.

840
00:42:43,740 --> 00:42:47,060
(Serve the People)

841
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:48,260
Hongling.

842
00:42:49,260 --> 00:42:49,740
What?

843
00:42:49,740 --> 00:42:50,580
Someone asked to see you.

844
00:42:51,060 --> 00:42:51,780
Who?

845
00:42:52,540 --> 00:42:53,340
There he is.

846
00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:59,460
(Keep Practicing)

847
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:08,640
♪I planted a seed by the sea♪

848
00:43:09,140 --> 00:43:12,900
♪Imagining what it would grow into♪

849
00:43:13,950 --> 00:43:17,690
♪Warm sunshine nursed its sprouting♪

850
00:43:18,150 --> 00:43:20,860
♪Then it glinted and blossomed♪

851
00:43:21,920 --> 00:43:25,490
♪In my dream, I found a bookmark♪

852
00:43:26,010 --> 00:43:29,840
♪Where a blue story was scribbled♪

853
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:34,700
♪In the story, I saw you and me♪

854
00:43:35,010 --> 00:43:37,990
♪You told the story and I listened♪

855
00:43:41,080 --> 00:43:44,580
♪I wish you a sweet life♪

856
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:48,830
♪Where you're never bothered♪

857
00:43:49,870 --> 00:43:53,380
♪I wish myself the vast sea♪

858
00:43:53,530 --> 00:43:56,960
♪Where I watch the tide ebb and flow♪

859
00:43:58,060 --> 00:44:01,560
♪May love warm all waiting men♪

860
00:44:02,540 --> 00:44:05,620
♪Telling stories in tears and smiles♪

861
00:44:06,650 --> 00:44:10,230
♪May the world be fantastic as always♪

862
00:44:10,230 --> 00:44:14,560
♪Casting its blue sunshine on the sea♪

863
00:44:14,930 --> 00:44:18,390
♪I wish you a sweet life♪

864
